---
---

<section class="border-y-[6px] border-dark-alt bg-dark mt-[100px]">
  <div class="max-w-[1440px] mx-auto px-[40px] py-[119px]">
    <!-- Section label -->
    <p class="font-tight text-[36px] leading-[46px] uppercase text-cream mb-[77px] max-w-[1130px] mx-auto px-[115px]">
      What people say after they've had the chat.
    </p>

    <!-- Quote -->
    <div class="relative max-w-[1130px] mx-auto px-[115px]">
      <!-- Navigation arrows -->
      <button class="absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-cream hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity" aria-label="Previous testimonial">
        <svg width="82" height="24" viewBox="0 0 82 24" fill="none">
          <path d="M0 12H80M0 12L12 2M0 12L12 22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
        </svg>
      </button>

      <blockquote class="font-tight text-[48px] leading-[74px] uppercase text-cream text-center">
        "JP suggested a fund that was super interesting to me, one I hadn't heard of and aligned with my goals. It was soooo fast to change things over. I would highly recommend. It is nice to know I have someone in my corner working with me to make me rich in retirement!"
      </blockquote>

      <button class="absolute right-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 text-cream hover:opacity-70 transition-opacity" aria-label="Next testimonial">
        <svg width="82" height="24" viewBox="0 0 82 24" fill="none">
          <path d="M82 12H2M82 12L70 2M82 12L70 22" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" />
        </svg>
      </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Attribution -->
    <p class="font-tight text-[36px] leading-[46px] uppercase text-cream text-center mt-[65px] max-w-[1130px] mx-auto">
      Laura te Kaat<br />Google Review — Fund recommendation & switch
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
